data.body:
@reduz 

This is to fix the issue I had when trying to detect unpress events for modifier keys. The commit message describes what I think is going on and how my change fixes it. I did check that pressing and unpressing shift gives the press/unpress events, after I update the input mapping action.

This also probably only works for Windows guessing from the file name. I could make the respective change on other platforms if needed.
